      "content": "So you're saying that by ensuring diversity, the journal is actually sacrificing its scientific rigor? That's a heavy accusation. Are you suggesting that the papers we're currently rejecting from non-Western institutions are actually higher quality in your view, and that replacing you with a more equitable system will make NatureReview lose its status as a top-tier journal?",
